These are Puzzles for 3x7 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-4-1::.
7 different games are played: monopoly, scrabble, backgammon, whist, billiard, mah-jongg, poker
The people have 7 different jobs:  analyst, manager, security-guard, fisherman, nurse, chef, entrepreneur
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: martial-arts, comedy, mystery, satire, adventure, romance, scientific
 1. the person playing poker is the chef##1
 2. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the left of the person watching satire movies##1
 3. the person playing billiard is on the far right##1
 4. the security-guard is on the left or right of the person watching adventure movies##3
 5. the person playing mah-jongg is the person playing mah-jongg##1
 6. the person watching comedy movies is the analyst##1
 7. the entrepreneur is on the left or right of the person playing poker##3
 8. the fisherman is on the left of the person watching satire movies##1
 9. the person playing scrabble is on the left or right of the chef##3
10. the person playing backgammon is on the right of the person watching adventure movies##1
11. the person playing mah-jongg is in the middle##1
12. the person watching mystery movies is on the left or right of the person watching satire movies##3
13. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the left or right of the manager##3
14. the person playing mah-jongg is in an even position##4
15. the person playing scrabble is on the left or right of the chef##3
16. the chef is in an odd position##4
17. the person watching mystery movies is on the right of the person playing whist##1
18. the entrepreneur is on the right of the person watching scientific movies##1
19. the person watching comedy movies is the person playing mah-jongg##1
20. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the right of the person watching comedy movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |       2       |    3     |     4      |     5     |    6     |    7     |
| Game      | poker  | scrabble | backgammon | mah-jongg        | monopoly       | whist | billiard     |
| Job   | chef   | entrepreneur       | security-guard  | analyst  | fisherman  | manager   | nurse  |
| Movie-Genre         | scientific | adventure         | romance  | comedy | martial-arts | satire  | mystery |

