 5. the person playing go is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
 6. the person playing backgammon is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
 7. the person playing go is the person who's birthday is in july##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in september is in an odd position##4
 9. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
10. the person playing snooker is the person who's birthday is in september##1
11. the person who's birthday is in april is on the right of the person playing go##1
12. the person who's birthday is in march is on the right of the person playing snooker##1
13. the person drinking tea is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in april##3
14. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left or right of the person playing billiard##3
15. the person who's birthday is in november is in an even position##4
16. the person drinking fanta is on the left or right of the person playing chess##3
17. the person drinking tea is in an even position##4
18. the person drinking sprite is the person who's birthday is in december##1
19. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left of the person who's birthday is in august##1
20. the person playing billiard is in the middle##1

